Introduction

Jung Hae-rim, popularly known as Elly, is a South Korean idol under Fantagio Entertainment. She made her debut as the lead vocalist of the girl group Weki Meki on August 8, 2017, with their first mini album "WEME".

Elly also participated in several survival shows. She first joined Produce 101 in 2016, where she ranked 47th. In 2023, she joined Kakao Entertainment's virtual reality show GIRL’S RE:VERSE. She made it to the top 20 but was eliminated at #19.

Later that year, she joined Mnet’s QUEENDOM PUZZLE. She reached the final round, but missed the cut, finishing at 11th place.
